    "name": "Rental Car System",
    "description": "AREX Recording/Replay target system: rental car management. Import into Postman and select a rental environment. Each request auto-generates an 18-digit traId and sends it in the X-Serial-No header so logs can be searched end-to-end. Complex transactions (RENT001-RENT015) produce HTTP sub-calls and JDBC activity. Simple transactions (RENT016-RENT030) are DB-only. Two environments: rental-base (port 20081) and rental-compare (port 20082) with intentional API differences.",
